items.title: Some wise words from my mother. Recently I've been reconsidering my path to med school, thinking maybe I could do other things with my life but I was reminded that it's probably only because life is hard right now - constant studying, barely any free time, etc. Sometimes we all need a reminder that even though things are hard, you shouldn't give up. It's okay to fail, it's okay to make a mistake;

mediaItems.title: Some wise words from my mother. Recently I've been reconsidering my path to med school, thinking maybe I could do other things with my life but I was reminded that it's probably only because life is hard right now - constant studying, barely any free time, etc. Sometimes we all need a reminder that even though things are hard, you shouldn't give up. It's okay to fail, it's okay to make a mistake; I mean, we are only human. But if what's waiting for you at the end of the road is what you truly want, keep your head up and keep fighting until you get there. Then one day, when you finally reach that goal, you'll look back and say "I'm glad I didn't give up". ‚ù§
